    "These systems can also detect when their false narratives are gaining or losing traction and adjust accordingly.",
    "This feedback loop allows for agile, adaptive tactics in almost real time.",
    "For instance, during an election, if a particular misleading talking point is not resonating, the AI may pivot to another line of attack that data shows is more compelling to the electorate.",
    "Cross-platform botnet deployment -modern campaigns rarely limit themselves to a single platform.",
    "Using AI, malicious actors create interconnected bot networks that operate on multiple social media sites simultaneously."
